<div class="wrapper">

  <!-- HEADER -->

  <div class="header-card">
    <div class="brand-line">Design the Game</div>
    <h1>Rob Gray is Coming<br>to <span>Ireland</span> — Are You In?</h1>
    <p>We're bringing one of the world's leading skill acquisition researchers and practitioners to Ireland for an exclusive one-day working session. Before we open booking, we want to make sure the right people are in the room.</p>
    <div class="scarcity-bar">
      <div class="scarcity-icon">🔒</div>
      <p class="scarcity-text"><strong>This form is invitation-only.</strong> We're keeping the event to a maximum of 35 people. Priority places go to those who register interest here before we go public.</p>
